Class PubAddSubCommand

public final class PubAddSubCommand extends PubSubCommandWithArgs
A subcommand for add name of the package into current project.

Supported option (excluded global options):

  • PubGitUrlOption
  • PubGitPathOption
  • PubGitRefOption
  • PubHostedUrlOption
  • PubSdkOption
  • PubPathOption
  • PubPrecompileOption
  • PubDevOption
  • PubOfflineOption
  • PubDryRunOption

1.0.0
